  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped kaffir lime leaves and saut\u00134 until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "add the hake fillets and cook until golden brown, about 3-4 minutes per side.",
    "add the fry-grind-rice-khao-khua and cook, stirring constantly, until lightly toasted, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "season with fish sauce and black pepper to taste.",
    "garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
